  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb4\u0bbf \u0b87\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Chicken meat also comes under price control",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Commerce, Trade and Food Security Minister Nalin Fernando said the government will take steps to impose a control price on chicken meat and a final decision on the matter will be reached this week.",
        "However, he said, if poultry farmers agree to lower prices, the control price is not necessary.",
        "Meanwhile, it is to be noted that the possible retail price of eggs has been fixed and published in the gazette with effect from midnight the day before yesterday. (R)"
      ],
